OL,4,C'carnage'
OL,6,FThe new school year is underway, but
OL,7,Ffor people living in Rhondda Cynon
OL,8,FTaf, the return to school has been
OL,9,Fdescribed as "carnage" following a
OL,10,Fchange to school transport.
OL,12,FThe new eligibility rules for free
OL,13,Fschool transport means only secondary
OL,14,Fschool and college pupils who live
OL,15,Fthree miles or further from their
OL,16,Fschool in the county borough are
OL,17,Fentitled to free school transport,
OL,18,Fwhich is a change from the previous
OL,19,Fthreshold of two miles or more.
