OL,6,FParents in RCT have described the
OL,7,Freturn to school as a "shambles" due
OL,8,Fto overcrowded buses, a large volume
OL,9,Fof traffic on the school run, and
OL,10,Fexcessive journey times.
OL,12,FA group of parents set up a Facebook
OL,13,Fgroup in 2024 when the council cut
OL,14,Fschool transport to try and fight for
OL,15,Fit back.
