OL,6,FLaura Hill was one of those parents.
OL,7,FShe told us: "We live 2.5 miles away
OL,8,Ffrom school. When we first started the
OL,9,Fcampaign me and my son walked it, it
OL,10,Ftook us an hour and 15 minutes to get
OL,11,Fto the school.
OL,13,F"They could save money anywhere else,
OL,14,Fthis is children's education and
OL,15,Fsafety. I have no words for it.
