OL,6,F"We've had a lot of messages from
OL,7,Fparents with anxiety and stress with
OL,8,Fhow they are getting their kids to
OL,9,Fschool. A lot of their children are
OL,10,Fstressing as well, having panic
OL,11,Fattacks."
OL,13,FCouncillor Karl Johnson, leader of
OL,14,FRhondda Cynon Taf's Welsh
OL,15,FConservatives, said seven dedicated
OL,16,Fschool buses serving one school had
OL,17,Fbeen removed, impacting 350 to 400
OL,18,Fpupils.
