OL,6,F"Putting pupils' safety over a few
OL,7,Fpounds and pence is really
OL,8,Fconcerning," he said. "I'm really
OL,9,Fconcerned with the volume of traffic
OL,10,Fthat a child could get injured."
OL,12,FThe distance threshold for free school
OL,13,Ftransport varies from council to
OL,14,Fcouncil. However, many share the same
OL,15,Frule, which is primary school pupils
OL,16,Fwho live two miles or more away from
OL,17,Ftheir school are eligible and
OL,18,Fsecondary school pupils who live three
OL,19,Fmiles or more.
