OL,6,FA spokesperson for Rhondda Cynon Taf
OL,7,FCouncil said: "This is the first week
OL,8,Fof the revised Home to School
OL,9,FTransport Policy being operational,
OL,10,Fand we are reviewing the effects of
OL,11,Fthe implementation.
OL,13,F"We will look at this feedback, and
OL,14,Fwill take any necessary practical
OL,15,Fsteps where required.
