OL,6,F"All secondary and post-16 learners
OL,7,Fare eligible for free transport in
OL,8,Fline with Welsh Government's Learner
OL,9,FTravel Measure, which is in place
OL,10,Facross 18 of 22 Welsh council areas.
OL,11,FThis means learners who live three
OL,12,Fmiles or more away from their place of
OL,13,Flearning still receive free transport.
OL,15,F"Our revised Home to School Transport
OL,16,FPolicy continues to still transport
OL,17,Fthousands of children more every week
OL,18,Fthan we are expected to, beyond the
OL,19,Fstatutory school transport
OL,20,Frequirements.
